column13:
you can never go wrong as it goes well with any casual attire. These brown sneakers brought to you by Carlton London make for a great accessory to any cool casual attire or sportswear. These laced men’s shoes come with high quality materials like synthetic fabric and PVC incorporated into them to make them withstand the tough environmental factors. The Logo Engraving on Left Side of the Body gives the shoe a snappy look. It also has a belt with a buckle at the back for an engaging look coupled with fabric detailing on the back and at its sides.

Carlton London shoes are always a class apart from the competition with its superior styling and comfort level in its products.

Footwear Care

Keep your precious Carlton London shoes in mint condition by wiping it regularly with a damp cloth and keeping it stored in a dry place when not in use. Regular brushing will also help keep dust away from the fabric seams.
